<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>MPIN Reset OTP</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #FFF9C4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #FBC02D;
            color: #000000;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #323232;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .otp-box {
            background: #D0EFFF;
            color: #000080;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #909090;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #0076DF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            MPIN Reset Request
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your MPIN. Use the OTP below to complete the process:</p>
            <div class="otp-box">
                <%= otp %>
            </div>
            <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Do not share it with anyone for security reasons.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            If you did not request this, please ignore this email.<br>
            <a href="#">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>